Package it.unifi.rc.httpserver.m5765968

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    MyHTTPFactory
    This class implements the HTTPFactory interface with the respective methods for creating objects.
    MyHTTPHandler1_0
    This class implements the HTTPHandler interface with the task of managing an HTTP/1.0 version request, creating a response of the same version otherwise it creates a null response.
    MyHTTPHandler1_1
    This class extends the HTTPHandler class 1_0 with the task of managing a Request HTTP/1.1 version as if it were an HTTP/1.0 version request for methods (GET, HEAD, POST).
    MyHTTPHandlerHost1_0
    This class extends the MyHTTPHandler1_0 class with the task to handle only requests whose host specified in their header rows matches the host specified by the handler.
    MyHTTPHandlerHost1_1
    This class extends the MyHTTPHandler1_1 class with the task to handle only requests whose host specified in their header rows matches the host specified by the handler.
    MyHTTPInputStream
    This class extends the HTTPInputStream class with the task of managing the reading of a Reply and Request object.
    MyHTTPOutputStream
    This class extends the HTTPOutputStream class with the task of managing the writing of a Reply and Request object.
    MyHTTPReply
    This class implements the HTTPReply interface and has the task of setting the elements of an HTTP Reply.
    MyHTTPRequest
    This class implements the HTTPRequest interface and has the task of setting the elements of an HTTP request.
    MyHTTPServer
    This class implements the HTTPServer interface with the respective methods to manage a server object.
    MyHTTPServerMain
    This class starts the operation of an HTTPServer object.
    MyHTTPThreadClient
    This class implements the Runnable interface with the respective methods to manage a client thread.
    MyHTTPThreadServer
    This class implements the Runnable interface with the respective methods to manage a server thread.
